                        <h2>Negative Marking or Penalty in TOEFL Exam</h2>
                        <p>The TOEFL iBT score ranges from 0 to 120. Each section is scored separately on a scale of 0 to 30, and the scores are combined to calculate the overall score. The scoring considers the number of correct answers and the difficulty level of the questions. There is no negative marking in TOEFL.</p>
                    </div>

