                            <li>Writing for an academic discussion task – 10 minutes duration – stating and supporting an opinion in an online classroom discussion.</li>
                            <li>Candidates have to type the responses on a computer keyboard.</li>
                            <li>It should take about 29 minutes to complete the writing section.</li>
                        </ul>
